✅Compatible with All Cooktops: An induction-suitable stainless steel base provides warp-resistant strength, enhanced durability, and versatility to use the nonstick cookware on any stovetop, including induction, gas, electric, and halogen

✅Even and Consistent Heat: this collection of essential pots and pans is crafted from durable aluminum for even heat distribution to reduce hot spots. With these induction pans, you could experience time-saving efficiency and pleasant cooking

✅Comfortable Grip Handles & Tempered Glass Lids: Our bakelite handle is designed to fit perfectly in the palm of your hand and stay comfortably cool on the stovetop, while shatter-resistant, tempered glass lid allows you to monitor cooking progress

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Love this set!!
reviews.reviewText: The media could not be loaded. Hubby got me this set after I got an induction stove top and I have to say they are such a great value. The quality looks so good and they are heavy-weight and well-made. They work wonderfully with my NUWAVE stove top. The clean-up is easy and they heat up quickly. Definitely recommend it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on August 7, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars I can see this set lasting for many years
reviews.reviewText: I love this set so much! It's very attractive (I got the black with the black and white speckled interior, and I just LOVE it), and it cleans like a dream.I can see this set lasting for many years with the use of silicone or wooden utensils. As with any nonstick pot and pan set, the key is to use non-metal utensils and to ensure that when you store them, you place a paper towel between the stacks to ensure the coating is not harmed. It will eventually give out, of course, but this set is really good and should last years. I'll update if anything changes with daily use.
